Single-database configuration


Create version file
```bash
alembic -c './config/alembic.ini' revision --autogenerate -m "name of the file"
alembic -c './config/alembic.ini' upgrade head
```


Apply all migration files to the database
```bash
alembic -c './config/alembic.ini' upgrade head
```


Downgrade one revision
This will revert the last file that was applied to the datatabse, file still going to be present
```bash
alembic -c './config/alembic.ini' downgrade head-1
```
